        | <b>Heavy:</b> #{demand.H.toLocaleString(locale)} lbs
        |
        |
        b <u>Ticket prices</u>
        |
        | <b>Economy:</b> $#{ticket.Y}
        | <b>Business:</b> $#{ticket.J}
        | <b>First:</b> $#{ticket.F}
        | <b>Large:</b> $#{ticket.L}
